snippet: Vietnam has released two high-profile dissidents, raising the number of democracy activists freed this month to three, officials said Monday.
abstract: Vietnamese officials say high-profile dissidents Vi Duc Hoi and Nguyen Tien Trung have been released, raising the number of democracy activists freed in April to three.
lead_paragraph: Vietnam has released two high-profile dissidents, raising the number of democracy activists freed this month to three, officials said Monday.

headline.main: Vietnam: Dissidents Freed Amid Trade Negotiations
